PROJECT TITLE
Mood to Music

---

PROBLEM STATEMENT
In today’s digital world, users often spend a lot of time searching for songs that match their mood. There is no simple and direct system that automatically provides music based on emotions. This project aims to develop a system that suggests songs according to the user's mood, making music selection faster and easier.

---

PROJECT OBJECTIVES

- Develop a mood-based music recommendation system
- Reduce time taken to search songs
- Provide simple and user-friendly interface
- Enable instant music playback
- Manage user data and preferences

---

MODULE LIST

- User Registration Module
- User Login Module
- Mood Selection Module
- Song Viewing Module
- Music Playback Module
- Search Module
- Favorites Module

